::Aerotaur::
       He winces as he passes through the wall of fire right behind Flicker.  
He beats his wings to put out their smoldering flames.  He continues to gain 
ground on Flicker through shear determination.  "Flicker.  Return her now.  
There's still time.  I will allow no harm to come to you."
